        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 4 at 6:20PM MDT until August 4 at 6:30PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>At 620 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 17 miles south of
Las Animas, or 23 miles southeast of North La Junta, moving southwest
at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Golf ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

This severe thunderstorm will remain over mainly rural areas of
southern Bent County.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
